{"tid":1837731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[品蔥轉載] 武漢肺炎上咗意大利 Twitter 嘅trend","createTime":"2020-01-23T18:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T18:09:07.000Z","uid":307203,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dd041d107341d8825ed4cd551740926af33c1de7","tid":1837731,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/12807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F12807&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=524010c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pincong.rocks/article/12807</a><br />\n<br />\n意大利人對武漢肺炎很關注，意大利推特趨勢第一 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FccOKb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFccOKb1.png&h=65b5e356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vp82ODT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvp82ODT.png&h=dffa798c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利的電動方程式要在中國3月21日舉行。 我覺得這個武漢的病毒比他們說的要嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVb7ZMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVb7ZMC.png&h=f4835923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國禁止出入武漢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JWPtFf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JWPtFf.png&h=de82684b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求你們幫我一下。 我沒有跟上這類新聞，但我知道好像在全中國有25例因病毒而導致的死亡。  （這可能是真的，因為中國審查一切）你們能給我解釋這個緊急情況嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WOmjQTN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWOmjQTN.png&h=b1e1178c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我是個混蛋嗎？ 我開玩笑的...因為您知道我很喜歡動物，我討厭那些不尊重動物的人...但這是另一回事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64mcrsD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64mcrsD.png&h=5579cf00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果他們這麼快就承認了而且採取了措施，我們可以確定問題比他們說的嚴重很多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLT6vUw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLT6vUw.png&h=b2bad648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我沒有收到警報，但情況非常嚴重。 意大利有一個非常有效的警戒系統，只要按程序來，不低估任何威脅就行，我們必須始終遵循預防原則。  （此人應該是意大利官員）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bOKhzK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bOKhzK.png&h=ec4358f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國人吃野生動物的行為百害而無一利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKw0Amy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKw0Amy.png&h=f61a1c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得中國肯定出了什麼大事，不然不會隔離3個城市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWtm4e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWtm4e7.png&h=bb9af566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不是意大利人，不過挺給台灣人面子的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQxOKfn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQxOKfn.png&h=9da95c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在中國，人們不能吃屎嘛，非要吃蛇，蝙蝠，狗，貓，異形和神奇寶貝？  ？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbhyVnj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbhyVnj.png&h=4a58ba29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伙計們，我們不是在開玩笑...我們也不是危言聳聽...這是農曆新年期間...住在中國的人都知道，只要打折人們甚至會為一升油而爭吵..這肯定不是為了 搶口罩！  （一段中國人搶菜視頻下的留言）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ns2vc9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fns2vc9e.png&h=a697212b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkEhCAT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkEhCAT.png&h=1885bfd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3WPtHx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3WPtHx.png&h=d19ecbc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MC8FAnw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMC8FAnw.jpg&h=cc2ef360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意大利人做的圖片來解釋這次武漢肺炎，大意就是說那個市場不干淨，很潮濕,是蛇傳給了人類（？？我都不知道是蛇）<br />\n<br />\n總結下：意大利人最反感的就是中國人吃野生動物這事"},{"pid":"99ac62897b7fb274ff0e2c9a2b0fea7b2141aa2e","tid":1837731,"uid":218,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"在中國，人們不能吃屎嘛，非要吃蛇，蝙蝠，狗，貓，異形和神奇寶貝？ ？<br />\nPokemon<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35d0fd65f30233bac6e7cde362e2976ee1855d4","tid":1837731,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:06:54.000Z","msg":"入來推十下！<br />\n<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"16a4d4f6a4fff75279652a6c3ccbeef4437340f1","tid":1837731,"uid":123765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99ac62897b7fb274ff0e2c9a2b0fea7b2141aa2e","tid":1837731,"uid":218,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"在中國，人們不能吃屎嘛，非要吃蛇，蝙蝠，狗，貓，異形和神奇寶貝？ ？<br />\nPokemon<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"pokemon真係笑撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd8cf95c3b02489f720c7b1995b435ff9a146a7","tid":1837731,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c35d0fd65f30233bac6e7cde362e2976ee1855d4","tid":1837731,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:06:54.000Z","msg":"入來推十下！<br />\n<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:14:04.000Z","msg":"幫你pin咗喇"},{"pid":"2ae8f4ba3be2f03ddd0ddab71e1ca3fd4717228e","tid":1837731,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd8cf95c3b02489f720c7b1995b435ff9a146a7","tid":1837731,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"